A jailmap with a high jump tower,

In every cell is something which can help the terrorists (Deagle,HE).

Counter-Terrorists have good chances to alive in the Security Tower.

There are secret chambers, gas chambers, healing room, swimming pool`s, Massenjail, Luxury Jail, 6 little Jails.

In the following release there are, alarm buttons (for CTS), football court, Roullette place, HE tennis court and much more.

We hope you have fun ;)

Greetz,
Kartracer and Lucy
